  "text": "Based on a comparison of different kernels in Supplementary Information, the RBF kernel performs on par with the SOAP-kernel. [CITATION_1] The resulting kernel matrices were used to predict the (free) adsorption energies of the test sets. The exponent of the radial distribution function γ and regularization parameter α were optimised by fivefold cross-validation.",
